July 2nd my first album “Pray For Me” comes out in honor of my grandmother Ann Bowling Nov 1931- June 2023. This one’s for you Gama 🖤 May she rest in peace. Presave in my bio xx
“Pray For Me” tonight 12 am EST 🖤

This collection of songs is the parts of my story I am ready to tell you. These are things that have broken me, hurt me, chewed me up and spit me out, but also shaped me. I encourage you to first listen to this project alone in a place where you feel comfortable.  I want you to take the time out of your day to cry to these songs and release your pain whether you relate to them or not. Hopefully I have included a song for each of you. Please go find yours. This album is dedicated to my grandmother who saved me without knowing she did. I hope to give you the same feeling of togetherness and rest in these words and know that you are not alone just as she did for me. May she rest in peace. Enjoy. (Link in bio)

Track 01: “The Actor”
I challenge you to reconsider your authenticity. Authenticity can come from an inauthentic place.
